name: Bibliographie du Levant on CD-ROM
description: A retrospective database devoted to works on the Middle East, in English, French and Latin. It contains some 12,000 entries, 10,000 authors and 400 images. The sources cited include those from the beginning of printing to recent scholarship. **This resource is only accessible in Bobst Library. To use this resource, stop by the 5th floor Reference Center.
